</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-88">
<term>5: </term> Conservation of mechanical energy is the characterizing feature of pure rolling. This is significant as mechanical energy is conserved even when friction is present.
</para>

